channel.title: Coding Ideas
channel.description:
I think this happens to alot of good writers.. I suppose it would go the same for coders.
"Writer's block"
We can't think of new ideas.
I've wasted over four hours trying to come up with an idea, putting off my homework.. Which I had two hours of.. Could have been done by now >_<
Anyway, if any other good coders want to code something, let me know
Also, I need some ideas, what does everyone want?
